column5: The Moses Lake Museum in Moses Lake Washington contains a small display of Japanese items. These items are from the Moses Lake-Yonezawa Sister City Exchange Program the Japan Airlines Training Center at the Grant County International Airport and the Japanese Agricultural Training Program.
